Very good tool.  A bit rough around the edge and slow at times, but
for the price you pay, it's OK (note : it's free).

I used it only once for a game of LnL.  It's as close as you can get
to FtF.  I know some people combines it with some audio connection
tools like Skype or TeamSpeak for a better experience.

And I also recommend the two (free again) software recoomended by GJK.
Cyberboard is a bit more crude, but has a lot of supporters in the
PBEM crowd AFAIK.
I haven't tested ZunTzu yet, but I heard a lot of good things about
it.

Cheers,

JeF.
